Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}弗洛瓦德家 迎宾馆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}卢纳帝国领 森林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 菲莉丝那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底上哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}大扫除之宴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有清醒的迹象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们的研究材料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放下就视为恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们会遭到神罚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 换谁都不想醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉浸在梦里反而更…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死啦 突然搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一点你的变态就要传染给那孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会传染才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你有何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你抛弃的私生子现在就指着你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为人父你打算怎么负责
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要随便脑补人家的人生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不是正被卢纳兵追杀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么瞎晃悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意儿扔路边碰巧被我捡来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想坐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧？路边？扔那儿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看绝对是哪家贵族那儿偷来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那孩子放上来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点你的变态要传染了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得送他去雷吉特村
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才去找马车的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你也会动脑子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在 白银
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去啊 白银
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃离那麻烦变态男
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 玩真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被丢下就跑啊 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 坑爹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送午餐来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 放那儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您放下工作 趁热吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决了这堆文件就吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这是罗兰德帝国元帅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉乌·柯洛姆交来的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我扣个这么无聊的职务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是本次升任要职的人员递交的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎大多是平民呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是刻意排除了贵族的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是无关出身 全凭实力选人的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他们在这短短几天内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就递交了这么多提案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了建设更美好的国家和民生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家正在发生变革
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么陛下就更应该保重贵体了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 好好吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我先告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在变革吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太平静了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的就算完事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有消息称阿克梅尔地区的贵族有可疑举动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克梅尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是弗洛瓦德家的领地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开端果然是阿克梅尔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}阿克梅尔地区 弗洛瓦德邸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 米兰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宾客已到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一声号令 全国的贵人都齐聚一堂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪儿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若没有你的人力 事情不会这么顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 我的能力远远比不上父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我引以为傲的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成长得如此俊美聪慧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够成为父亲的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也感到无上光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戏还请保留一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人们还在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日承蒙各位大驾光临 不胜感激
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚宴会的主办人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这位斯提亚里德公爵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及吾父卡拉尔·弗洛瓦德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衷心感谢各位赏光接受我们的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而贤明如各位 想必已经知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我们今日要聚集在此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了教训那个嚣张的小鬼 席恩·阿斯塔尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢对我们贵族视若无睹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把他拖下王位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能再忍气吞声了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说他是王族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是下贱的狗杂种
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那种人当国王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家只有死路一条
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前一定要推翻他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划已经制定完备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合与前王有深交的卢纳帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把阿斯塔尔拉下台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情由制定计划的米兰来说明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 米兰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先希望到场的各位做一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们去死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗影现形
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 米兰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成你连我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直耐心等待着这一天的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从被你收养那一刻开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:10:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的地从一开始就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你不过是我达成目的的一颗棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棋子…这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到你时你才五岁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时 弗洛瓦德家的主人是你兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这位兄长以及族里的其他人都接连身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因意外事故
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你掌握了弗洛瓦德家的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是你杀了…族里的所有人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩下你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢 慢着米兰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也听腻了你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您的合作 斯提亚里德公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福 我得以将不安分子一网打尽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请记住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是您敢背叛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会背叛的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁敢和您作对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不敢反抗您…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能从我的暗影之下生还
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是何许人也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然在这里 当然是罗兰德贵族…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一头桃色的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南大陆基本是没人会有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然精明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪国人士？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看起来像是有问必答的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就请你回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我还有工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不大想在这里消耗力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来者之兽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然拥有和我一样的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我真是不想和你作战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到我的来兽竟然只有这点反应的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是头一次见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我已经很惊讶了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的存在本身已是出乎意料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还杀了斯提亚里德公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 公爵幕后还有黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.68,0:12:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵他并和你的国家串通的黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在罗兰德吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还是早点回去的好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:13:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便把你的戒指带走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾所求烧原
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账 来兽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,势均力敌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来很难分个高下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你应该已经发现了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你用不了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一用就会暴露自己的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然戒指的力量不相上下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以用魔法 就占据了优势
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间大厅的门全都关闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃离必须用那来兽破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而只要你有一只兽去开门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的兽就会趁机咬破你的喉咙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你一定没什么朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你作何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要投降 还是冒着被杀的风险逃命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:14:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两者都免了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「歼眼」之结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这个就是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让暗影去开门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背后的防守就会削弱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太轻敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会死在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧倒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯洛姆元帅阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿再说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗影现形
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯洛姆元帅阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的暗影也撑不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 柯洛姆元帅阁下怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是奉席恩之命来的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我才不想来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是陛下？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 贵为元帅的您怎会孤身一人前来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然带了兵的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩那家伙说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会遇到反击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老是自作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到你这张脸我就想一老拳打过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一个人先来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您刚才说并不想来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又扔下士兵们抢先过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了吗 我赶这么急就是为了揍你一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而不但没揍还救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还说我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还是要道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若没有您 我早已死于非命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢救命之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那蓝色火焰是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们的战争…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}王宫 谒见室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯洛姆元帅与弗洛瓦德中将
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正朝城堡前来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 很有意思的攻击方式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪电之兽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也只是有趣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我面前是毫无用处的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若明知如此还要骚扰我国的国王…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只好请你消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请转告你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若胆敢对罗兰德下手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.42,0:17:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有什么下场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气息消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:17:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是抓住他比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端由你定夺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我也能给你抓回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好 你还没坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动乱的时代即将来临吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有你这个国王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信这个国家能够幸存下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我无法守护这个国家到底呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就杀了你另立一个更有能力的新王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你尽管放手去做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手去做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西在蠢蠢欲动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑之一族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这个国家怎么全是怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我执行任务失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}卢纳帝国 王之间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亲善大使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的国王说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:19:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和卢纳帝国联手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会说不吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卢纳帝国已经和罗兰德缔结同盟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是串通罗兰德贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算推翻现在的罗兰德王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 和你串通的斯提亚里德公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经死在我们的同伴手下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢 罗兰德已经靠不住了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那我再问一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您同意联手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们加斯塔克帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 给您点时间考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们另外还有任务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静候您的佳音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 库
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 所以我才放不下斯伊哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好歹也独立点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起 库
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 自己想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五秒之内回答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5 4 3 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 记得是什么村来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷吉特村
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找有复写眼的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}卢纳帝国领 森林
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是烦人的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快被追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才真戳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞吧 罪人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.13,0:20:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情跳出死亡之舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为能从我们的神明手中逃脱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么神明 开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乞求无所不在的神明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐可悲的吾等破魔之刃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾献上契约之文
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放舞于天空的光之魔兽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔亚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在睡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要回雷吉特村吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还要把那叫可可的女孩一起带走才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带走？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在那村里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.11,0:21:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔亚和可可都不会幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要带他们去一个可以过安稳日子的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵又要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快舞 舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 不要 别戳 痛死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入国审查好像很严呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史特欧尔的军队好像来了很多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}史特欧尔皇国 国境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为正在和加斯塔克打仗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克好像很强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 大史特欧尔帝国怎么可能输给那种小国
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗兰德 卡斯拉 艾斯特里奥 史特欧尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.06,0:23:23.56,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}制作：akira 安静の云
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们身边的事就已经够麻烦的了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.57,0:23:26.90,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an8}漫游字幕组\Nhttp://popgo.net/bbs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大陆北方？加斯塔克？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么远的国家谁管得着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}北方的勇者王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要特地跑出来 烦死啦
